{"tid":2053050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［等睇高官同佢D仔女加入］大頭Man帶頭撕毀自己本BNO","createTime":"2020-06-06T03:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T06:48:29.000Z","uid":22556,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d26cd2f9e5d456b12ae0d2868abd42db7387378c","tid":2053050,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:21:27.000Z","msg":"今早（6 日），建制派石房有（大波 Man）、高松傑、公民力量林宇星等人到英國駐港總領事館示威，譴責英國「干涉中國內政」，又指香港人不需要 BNO，他們並且當場將自己各自的 BNO 撕毀。<br />\n<br />\n林宇星表示，「BNO 對於香港人嚟講只係旅遊證件」，而且不能夠正確代表香港人的國民身份，「我哋已經回歸祖國，睇唔到原因點解要續 BNO」。林又說，希望英國不要再在 BNO 議題上「出口術」，企圖破壞中港關係，以及傷害中港兩地人民感情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CaTtSH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCaTtSH9.jpg&h=676ef129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3146155442136721/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3146155442136721%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdxwmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=8b47c8ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3146155442136721/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55c3e962ece20d4b0358d6fe98621e990595528","tid":2053050,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"鬥紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b111066dfaa9cf1a5ba5ce3576a23b246d4bacde","tid":2053050,"uid":322274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"幾時撕埋林鄭屋企人本BC"},{"pid":"0e503172c4e8c8f1aaad29ff1c80325aa6b6b114","tid":2053050,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"鬥藍鬥紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70bfbdf17a3aa976991901f7dd12458263784b7","tid":2053050,"uid":152476,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":